The paper focuses on unsupervised learning of visual embeddings, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the potential for these unsupervised approaches to further artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and the use of clustering objectives (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of neural networks (cs.NE) in their approach.
